146  SafeFunction static inline void Pause(bool Loop = false)
147  {
148  do
149  {
150 #if defined(__amd64__) || defined(__i386__)
151  asmv("pause");
152 #elif defined(__aarch64__)
153  asmv("yield");
154 #endif
155  } while (Loop);

161  SafeFunction static inline void Stop()
162  {
163  while (1)
164  {
165 #if defined(__amd64__) || defined(__i386__)
166  asmv("CPUStopLoop:\n"
167  "cli\n"
168  "hlt\n"
169  "jmp CPUStopLoop");
170 #elif defined(__aarch64__)
171  asmv("msr daifset, #2");
172  asmv("wfe");
173 #endif
174  }
175  }
